interpretation: The "motorway" card represents a journey, both physical and metaphorical. This card encourages you to keep moving forward, despite obstacles or challenges in your path. It may indicate a long and winding road ahead, but also the potential for speed and progress. Trust in your own direction and don't be afraid to take risks. This card can also suggest the need for a change of scenery or a new adventure. Keep your eyes on the road and stay focused on your destination.
